                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - L
                   ====================================

                                   LAPD
                                   ====



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Energy   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(54430,0) zxampoke(57521,0) zxampoke(57806,0)"}      54430,0:57521,0:57806,0
@{"Infinite Ammo     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(50241,0) zxampoke(54248,0) zxampoke(50254,80)"}      50241,0:54248,0:50254,80
@{"Infinite Fast Ammo" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(54260,0)"}      54260,0
@{"Men To Kill = x   " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(49972,1)"}      49972,x (x= 1-255)


                         This POKE works for both 48K and 128K versions.


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
